SELECT viewname, reloptions
FROM pg_views v
JOIN pg_class c ON c.relname = v.viewname
WHERE v.schemaname = 'public' AND v.viewname = 'tarea_activa';
-- Esperado: reloptions contiene security_invoker=true

-- RPC eliminar ya no hace DELETE (cuerpo con eliminada_en)
SELECT pg_get_functiondef(p.oid) LIKE '%eliminada_en%'
FROM pg_proc p
JOIN pg_namespace n ON p.pronamespace = n.oid
WHERE n.nspname = 'public' AND proname = 'sgtd_eliminar_tarea_con_motivo';
-- Esperado: true
```

**CLI one-liner (034 aplicada):**

```bash
npx @insforge/cli db query "SELECT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_schema = 'public' AND table_name = 'tarea' AND column_name = 'eliminada_en') AS migration_034_ok"
```

